# Getting Started

## Simple date & time picker implemented in svelte.

Features:

- Datepicker
- Timepicker (with meridian support)
- Various format
- Keyboard navigation
- Includes `<input>` element
- Custom element
- Validator action for `<input>` using `svelte-use-forms` (optional)
- Easily themable

## Installation

Run this command

```bash
	npm install svelty-picker
```

